{"tid":1365062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［公安關口check手機］小心電話","createTime":"2019-07-25T13:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T15:19:14.000Z","uid":266325,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f13adfbb52af3d4db4e6dca3138b9072feff2c49","tid":1365062,"uid":266325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:48:34.000Z","msg":"從來唔番大陸既唔洗睇<br />\n岩先有個朋友係皇崗番落黎香港 係過大陸關口前 有公安要check書包同睇手機 包括微信同訊息 或者有其他<br />\n我朋友話好奇既係之前都唔會查 而家就嚴左咁多 <br />\n我諗緊係咪關反送中事 但如果咁點解唔等佢入大陸個下已經查 要等人番香港個下先查 係咪驚人係大陸宣傳啲咩野？純粹多疑問下 <br />\n自己過關大陸前準備好手機啲野 盡量del到就del啦 廢事又被失蹤 <br />\n歡迎討論"},{"pid":"a9ed419175af1f13286de73eaca83b928af4479b","tid":1365062,"uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"仲返大陸就抵死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f244e897b3380681dd0df57617ffc166b6d7f7c","tid":1365062,"uid":266325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7751963500c0b696068eb35f8e70a41b9abf9cb8","tid":1365062,"uid":266325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a9ed419175af1f13286de73eaca83b928af4479b","tid":1365062,"uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"仲返大陸就抵死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:51:19.000Z","msg":"接觸過啲群比公安睇到會點你覺得"},{"pid":"02aba777eaa9b9d959b8f14ca4e903e6036dff1b","tid":1365062,"uid":266325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:51:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e634130875a1012e19b64dd7e0f131dd2f39eeaa","tid":1365062,"uid":266325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"880df3991e0cbfd80e71c54155f8269acc508ac1","tid":1365062,"uid":266325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b625f1b4165ddeb1d5d7064ae22e2bf35f01